<th class="navbox-group" style="white-space:nowrap;">Université catholique de Louvain<br />(1835-1968)</th>
<td class="navbox-list navbox-even" style=""><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r178773919"/><div class="liste-verticale-horizontale">
<ul><li><b>Institutions&#160;:</b>
